00:20:54,772 --> 00:20:55,452
pretty straightforward,

501
00:20:55,532 --> 00:20:57,293
but we knew we'd be using mocap as a base

502
00:20:57,333 --> 00:20:59,714
for a lot of the combat animation suite.

